"title": "8355: understanding",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8355: understanding",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God-given perception of the nature and meaning of things, resulting in sound judgment and decision-making; in particular the ability to discern spiritual truth and to apply it to human disposition and conduct.</p>\n<h2>The source of understanding</h2>\n<h3>Understanding belongs to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:13\">JOB 12:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:5\">PSA 136:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:5\">PSA 147:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:19\">PRO 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:15\">JER 51:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:15\">JER 15:15</a> <em>God's understanding gives rise to compassion.</em></p>\n<h3>Understanding is a gift from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:6\">PRO 2:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:24\">ISA 29:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:29\">1KI 4:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:36\">JOB 38:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:3-Isa32:4\">ISA 32:3–32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:17\">DAN 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:21\">DAN 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:30\">DAN 2:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:22\">DAN 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:21\">ROM 15:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:15\">ISA 52:15</a></p>\n<h2>Understanding spiritual truth</h2>\n<h3>Understanding truth about God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:5\">PRO 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:10\">PRO 9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:21\">ISA 40:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:28\">ISA 40:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:10\">ISA 43:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:24\">JER 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:38\">JHN 10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:20\">ROM 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>Understanding God's purposes</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:6\">DEU 9:6</a> <em>God's reason for choosing Israel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:19\">1CH 28:19</a> <em>God's plans for the temple</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:10-Job34:11\">JOB 34:10–34:11</a> <em>the reason for Job's suffering</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:16-Ps73:17\">PSA 73:16–73:17</a> <em>God's dealings with the wicked</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:1-Isa57:2\">ISA 57:1–57:2</a> <em>God's purpose in taking the righteous</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:12-Jer9:13\">JER 9:12–9:13</a> <em>the reason for the exile</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:20\">JER 23:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer30:24\">JER 30:24</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:15-Dan8:16\">DAN 8:15–8:16</a> <em>God's purposes in history</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:17\">EPH 5:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:9\">COL 1:9</a></p>\n<h3>Understanding God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:73\">PSA 119:73</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:45\">LUK 24:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:8\">NEH 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:12\">NEH 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:27\">PSA 119:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:125\">PSA 119:125</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:15\">MAT 24:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:14\">MRK 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:27\">LUK 24:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:30-Acts8:31\">ACT 8:30–8:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:16\">JHN 12:16</a></p>\n<h3>Understanding Jesus Christ's teaching</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:11\">MAT 13:11</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:11\">MRK 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:10\">LUK 8:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:12\">MAT 16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:13\">MAT 17:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:33\">MRK 4:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:17\">MRK 8:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:22\">JHN 2:22</a></p>\n<h3>Understanding God's salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:18\">EPH 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:20\">ISA 41:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:11\">ROM 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:9\">EPH 1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:4\">EPH 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:17-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:17–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:6\">PHM 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>Human understanding is limited</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:26\">JOB 36:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:5\">JOB 37:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:5\">PRO 3:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:14\">JOB 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:29\">JOB 36:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:3\">JOB 42:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:24\">PRO 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:5\">ECC 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:13-Isa40:14\">ISA 40:13–40:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:8-Isa55:9\">ISA 55:8–55:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor13:12\">1CO 13:12</a></p>\n<h2>Gaining understanding</h2>\n<h3>Through faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:3\">HEB 11:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:8-Matt16:9\">MAT 16:8–16:9</a></p>\n<h3>Through God's Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:12\">1CO 2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:12\">1CH 28:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:8\">JOB 32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13-John16:15\">JHN 16:13–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:17\">EPH 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Through God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:130\">PSA 119:130</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:6\">DEU 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:10\">PSA 111:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:2\">DAN 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:9\">JHN 20:9</a></p>\n<h3>Through wise teaching</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:3\">PSA 49:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:8-Job8:10\">JOB 8:8–8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:2\">PRO 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:1\">PRO 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:32\">PRO 15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:9\">ECC 12:9</a></p>\n<h2>Lack of understanding of spiritual truth</h2>\n<h3>Not knowing God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:3\">ISA 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:28-Deut32:29\">DEU 32:28–32:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa27:11\">ISA 27:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:22\">JER 4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:19\">ROM 10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:21\">DEU 32:21</a></p>\n<h3>Lack of understanding due to hardened hearts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:4\">DEU 29:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:9-Isa6:10\">ISA 6:9–6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:4\">JOB 17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:18\">ISA 44:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:8\">ISA 48:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:21\">JER 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:2\">EZK 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:13-Matt13:15\">MAT 13:13–13:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:11-Mark4:12\">MRK 4:11–4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:10\">LUK 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:52\">MRK 6:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:40\">JHN 12:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:26-Acts28:27\">ACT 28:26–28:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:18\">EPH 4:18</a></p>\n<h3>Not understanding God's purposes</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:5\">PSA 82:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:6-Ps92:7\">PSA 92:6–92:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:13\">ISA 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:12\">ISA 19:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:12\">MIC 4:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:56\">LUK 12:56</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:8\">1CO 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Not understanding Jesus Christ's teaching</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:19\">MAT 13:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:13\">MRK 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:32\">MRK 9:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:32-John4:33\">JHN 4:32–4:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:27\">JHN 8:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:13\">JHN 11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:18\">JHN 16:18</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:50\">LUK 2:50</a> <em>by Jesus Christ's parents</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:20-John2:21\">JHN 2:20–2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:51-John6:52\">JHN 6:51–6:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:43\">JHN 8:43</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:11\">JHN 4:11</a> <em>by the Samaritan woman</em></p>\n<h2>Understanding people and situations</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:32\">1CH 12:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:13\">EST 1:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:1\">JOB 13:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:5\">PRO 20:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:24\">JHN 7:24</a></p>\n<h2>Understanding languages</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:7\">GEN 11:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:49\">DEU 28:49</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:5\">PSA 81:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:11\">ISA 36:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:6\">ACT 2:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:2\">1CO 14:2</a></p>\n<h2>Those who have understanding</h2>\n<h3>The wise</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:29\">DEU 32:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs4:29\">1KI 4:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:14\">PRO 8:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos14:9\">HOS 14:9</a></p>\n<h3>Good leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:15\">JER 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:13\">DEU 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:12\">1CH 22:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:22\">2CH 30:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:2\">PRO 28:2</a>PRO <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:16\">28:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:11\">ISA 56:11</a></p>\n<h2>The results of understanding</h2>\n<h3>Seeking God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:2\">PSA 14:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps53:2\">PSA 53:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:11\">ROM 3:11</a></p>\n<h3>Obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:34\">PSA 119:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:28\">NEH 10:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:9\">PSA 32:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:100\">PSA 119:100</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:7\">PRO 28:7</a></p>\n<h3>Taking the right path</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:9\">PRO 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:104\">PSA 119:104</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:21\">PRO 15:21</a></p>\n<h3>Life</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:144\">PSA 119:144</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:22\">PRO 16:22</a></p>\n<h3>Sensible living</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:28\">JOB 28:28</a> <em>avoidance of evil</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:12\">PRO 11:12</a> <em>slowness to criticise</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:11\">PRO 12:11</a> <em>conscientious labour</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:15\">PRO 13:15</a> <em>winning favour</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:27\">PRO 17:27</a> <em>showing restraint and an even temper</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:13\">JAS 3:13</a> <em>good deeds and humility</em></p>\n<h2>The results of a lack of understanding</h2>\n<h3>Foolish behaviour</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:32\">PRO 6:32</a> <em>committing adultery</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov7:7\">PRO 7:7</a> <em>being easily seduced</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:18\">PRO 17:18</a> <em>making rash commitments</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:1-Prov18:2\">PRO 18:1–18:2</a> <em>selfishness and self-importance</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:30-Prov24:31\">PRO 24:30–24:31</a> <em>idleness leading to ruin</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:11\">HOS 4:11</a> <em>Drunkenness clouds understanding.</em></p>\n<h3>Death</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:21\">PRO 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:16\">PRO 21:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:14\">HOS 4:14</a></p>",
